OL,7,FGold medal winning track and field
OL,8,Fathletes at this summer's Games will
OL,9,Feach receive $50,000 (#39,400) in
OL,10,Fprize money, World Athletics has
OL,11,Fannounced.
OL,13,FThe governing body unveiled a $2.4
OL,14,Fmillion (#1.89m) prize pot for the
OL,15,FParis Games on Wednesday morning - a
OL,16,Fmove which makes it the first
OL,17,Finternational sport federation to
OL,18,Faward prize money at an Olympics.
