OL,7,FWorld Athletics president Sebastian
OL,8,FCoe hailed the development as a
OL,9,F"pivotal moment", saying it
OL,10,Funderscores the body's "commitment to
OL,11,Fempowering the athletes and
OL,12,Frecognising the critical role they
OL,13,Fplay in the success of any Olympic
OL,14,FGames".
OL,16,FHe said it was a continuation of a
OL,17,Fjourney that began in 2015 "which sees
OL,18,Fall the money World Athletics receives
OL,19,Ffrom the International Olympic
OL,20,FCommittee (IOC) for the Olympic Games
OL,21,Fgo directly back into our sport".
