OL,7,F"We started with the Olympic dividend
OL,8,Fpayments to our member federations,
OL,9,Fwhich saw us distribute an extra five
OL,10,Fmillion dollars a year on top of
OL,11,Fexisting grants aimed at athletics
OL,12,Fgrowth projects, and we are now in a
OL,13,Fposition to also fund gold medal
OL,14,Fperformances for athletes in Paris,
OL,15,Fwith a commitment to reward all three
OL,16,Fmedallists at the LA28 Olympic Games,"
OL,17,FLord Coe added.
