OL,7,F"While it is impossible to put a
OL,8,Fmarketable value on winning an Olympic
OL,9,Fmedal, or on the commitment and focus
OL,10,Fit takes to even represent your
OL,11,Fcountry at an Olympic Games, I think
OL,12,Fit is important we start somewhere and
OL,13,Fmake sure some of the revenues
OL,14,Fgenerated by our athletes at the
OL,15,FOlympic Games are directly returned to
OL,16,Fthose who make the Games the global
OL,17,Fspectacle that it is."
