OL,7,FThe awarding of prize money will be
OL,8,Fsubject to ratification, which will
OL,9,Finclude medal-winning athletes
OL,10,Fundergoing and clearing the usual anti-
OL,11,Fdoping checks.
OL,13,FThe modern Olympics originated as an
OL,14,Famateur sports event and the IOC does
OL,15,Fnot award prize money.
OL,17,FHowever, many medalists receive
OL,18,Fpayments from their countries'
OL,19,Fgovernments, national sports bodies or
OL,20,Ffrom sponsors.
